{"tid":1238474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以印傳單幫各餐廳宣傳","createTime":"2019-06-17T23:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T02:57:11.000Z","uid":51829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2af9069b24bebb982809241dfbb3a321ff4ecf90","tid":1238474,"uid":51829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:52:09.000Z","msg":"有巴單整咗個全港地圖，但咁多記唔到嘛，又難俾其他人知<br />\n如果我哋印傳單分區咁派，每區只印出嗰區餐單，咁嗰區人士就易記好多<br />\n張傳單唔使寫咩，就例如紅磡區A餐廳，B餐廳，C餐廳<br />\n大大隻字: 他們支持警察，反抗市民全是暴徒<br />\n然後再加埋證據圖<br />\n<br />\n咁就夠，咩都唔使講，收到嘅人自然明，佢屌鳩你搞事仲可以話，支持警察係好事我當然幫你宣揚，我哋都支持警察架"},{"pid":"c5738949d1be40d1ef3145d3c4f8881bb8e4a0b7","tid":1238474,"uid":51829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:52:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f19079e88adc5bac4ad2f6747532bd70998e5a09","tid":1238474,"uid":51829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:55:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4d243e44ccb77948a42f38a2cf2d7563833700a","tid":1238474,"uid":51829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:56:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1ce54fd4b10a6dcac8291775e2a9d8972f3509a","tid":1238474,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:03:29.000Z","msg":"為左反映各商戶對警察嘅支持，應該推出一個「優質撐警商戶計劃」，只要小商戶願意出少少綿力去表達對警察嘅支持，都可以獲得一個「支持警察貼紙」俾佢地貼喺門口當眼處，讓市民都可以知道佢地對警務人員嘅支持同埋愛"},{"pid":"f8151599002a0155e65800423e522a3d29ca223c","tid":1238474,"uid":7494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:07:57.000Z","msg":"撐"},{"pid":"f38a0d7bb12ba10dbc130fa112bc99e7967091af","tid":1238474,"uid":51829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:49:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88261a138d723abb5e74be516aef2db62e643e30","tid":1238474,"uid":261430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:50:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a7ed33bfffbb6c609b352dd30b6b5912148e08d","tid":1238474,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019